7 Tag Merging
*************

‘howm-todo-add-project-tag’ preserves any Org-style tag block that
already trails the line.

Before                               After (adding ‘garden’)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
‘TODO [A1] mow lawn’                 ‘TODO [A1] mow lawn :garden:’
‘TODO [A1] mow lawn :home:’          ‘TODO [A1] mow lawn :home:garden:’
‘TODO [A1] mow lawn                  ‘TODO [A1] mow lawn
:home:outdoor:’                      :home:outdoor:garden:’
‘TODO [A1] mow lawn :garden:’        ‘TODO [A1] mow lawn :garden:’ (no
                                     change)


