9 Testing
*********

Run the test suite from the source directory:

     make test

The Makefile invokes Emacs in batch mode and runs the suite from
‘howm-todo-tests.el’.  SQLite-related tests are skipped automatically
when neither the built-in sqlite library nor the ‘sqlite3’ shell is on
‘PATH’.


